v2.0 – Enhanced NASA APOD Explorer

This major update turns the basic NASA Picture of the Day Viewer into an interactive, educational experience.

✨ New Features

⭐ Save and view Favorites

🎲 Random NASA Picture button

⬇ Download image in HD

🌓 Dark / Light mode toggle

🔊 Voice narration of picture details

⏮⏭ Easy navigation through previous and next days

🪐 Improvements

Clean, mobile-friendly design using TailwindCSS

Persistent theme and favorite storage via localStorage

Better error handling and smoother API integration

Result:
A more engaging, accessible, and feature-packed space exploration app built on NASA’s open APOD API. 🌌
